UPDATE `quest_template` SET `Details`='Can you believe what the tyrannical bureaucrats in charge of Stormwind have done? They have declared that Shellcoin investments are subject to taxation! It\'s an outrage!\r\n\r\nWe can\'t possibly continue to operate in this city under these rules. Something has to be done! Will you help us change their minds?\r\n\r\nGo to Stormwind Keep and speak to the legislators there. Help nudge them in the right direction by giving them a taste of the prosperity Shellcoin provides. Five gold ought to be enough.' WHERE `entry`=39986;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `Details`='You may have secured the House of Nobles\' support, but we cannot overturn the law by ourselves. To guarantee success at the next legislative council, your motion must have the church\'s support as well.\r\n\r\nI hear that Bishop DeLavey is great enjoyer of expensive rum. If you were to present him with a few bottles of the stuff, he\'d agree with anything you have to say.' WHERE  `entry`=39987;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `EndText`='Give 5 gold to Highlord Bolvar Fordragon.' WHERE  `entry`=39988;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `EndText`='Give 5 gold to Lord Baurles K. Wishock.' WHERE  `entry`=39986;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `Details`='You say you\'re worried about some unholy new law? Fear not, $n, I shall speak out against it at the next legislative session. Everything for a good friend of the holy light like you! Hic!\r\n\r\nBut for the bill to pass, it would still need the royal seal of approval. Tell his highness what you told me, and that you have mine and Lord Wishock\'s support. Maybe throw in five gold for good measure!' WHERE  `entry`=39988;
UPDATE `quest_template` SET `OfferRewardText`='What\'s that you are carrying the bag. Something is moving inside, take it out!' WHERE  `entry`=39983;
